{"tid":2037192,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「港區國安法」未立法已收緊","createTime":"2020-05-27T00:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T00:46:44.000Z","uid":85502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e2527d5ecea3f89acc348a09d5307d0542db4d42","tid":2037192,"uid":85502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:45:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528451-20200526.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528451-20200526.htm&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8Uyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=89c3a04c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528451-20200526.htm&h=e1563c7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528451-20200526.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n全國人大下午審議常委會建立「港區國安法」和健全執行機制的決定草案修改稿，據了解，草案有數處修改。<br />\n<br />\n修改稿獲會議主席團開會通過，據了解，決定草案原本提到「禁止危害國安的行為」的相關内容，最新版本都改為「禁止危害國安的行為和活動」，增加「活動」的概念。<br />\n<br />\n至於較受爭議的第4項決定，有關中央維護國安的機關可能在港設立機構的内容，則沒有改動。<br />\n<br />\n根據議程，人大星期四早上會審議決定草案的建議表決稿，當天下午在閉幕會上進行表決。"},{"pid":"c28f982dfa893386fc3f793d1cbb29f9b9ee09f3","tid":2037192,"uid":85502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:46:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}